                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12526221" author="stack" created="Mon, 10 Sep 2007 18:59:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a patch to change two parameters.  Tables are now created and dropped in 10 seconds rather than 30.  I also tried these params on our small cluster under load.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
     &amp;lt;name&amp;gt;hbase.client.pause&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;
-    &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;30000&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;
+    &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;10000&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;
     &amp;lt;description&amp;gt;General client pause value.  Used mostly as value to wait
     before running a retry of a failed get, region lookup, etc.&amp;lt;/description&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;
@@ -102,7 +102,7 @@
   &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;property&amp;gt;
     &amp;lt;name&amp;gt;hbase.regionserver.msginterval&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;
-    &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;10000&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;
+    &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;3000&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12526254" author="stack" created="Mon, 10 Sep 2007 20:18:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Trying against hudson&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
